{"tid":1232956,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"重要！ 617 大型嘉年華會 通訊方法","createTime":"2019-06-16T16:58:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T17:31:16.000Z","uid":191290,"like":53,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1a63442934e30f3931a286acb4f1a530c736cb27","tid":1232956,"uid":191290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:58:35.000Z","msg":"此為share account. 借朋友出post<br />\n<br />\n前言：<br />\n<br />\n我發夢去海洋公園嘉年華其中一個好大問題係太多人網絡 幾乎癱瘓<br />\n消息傳遞 <span style=\"font-size: large;\">非常唔流通</span><br />\n所以急需改善<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\nProposal:<br />\n<br />\n臨時臨急搵唔到海洋公園地圖<br />\n所以求其用住一張先<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/17/004138_0bfeeea25ac3816ea3da93f2bcb722d6.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F17%2F004138_0bfeeea25ac3816ea3da93f2bcb722d6.jpeg&h=92ec86f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">紅色</span>標記為六個嘉年華主要攤位<br />\n黑色為大型攤位<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">建議 1</span></span><br />\n<br />\n六個攤位集合後選兩位店員<br />\n連同通訊員<br />\n於指定時間(例如-12:00) 去黑色大型攤位 集合互相溝通 交換聯絡方式並確認溝通方法<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後因為對講機同通訊app都唔可靠<br />\n加上嘉年華太多參加人士大家對場內資訊非常貧乏 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">建議2</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如圖中藍色交叉位 每個交叉為設置兩名主通訊員 用特定頻道溝通 再加上<br />\n配以4色顏色旗幟 （可以用文具店大塊顏色卡版） + 6個大型攤位字母牌互通消息<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/17/004527_00a120d7ad147b1fe28e3da48880bb7e.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F17%2F004527_00a120d7ad147b1fe28e3da48880bb7e.jpeg&h=0a52d23d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">黃色 保安開始迫近需要增援</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">紅色 危險需要退後</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">藍色 暫時安全</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">綠色 預備推進 各方戒備</span></span><br />\n<br />\n例如： A攤位 見到保安開始接近<br />\n龍和道通訊員需要舉起<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">黃色</span>+A字牌</span> <br />\n其他通訊員同樣以黃色＋A牌relay全場<br />\n<br />\n或者 D攤位 玩家希望入去大樓涼冷氣<br />\n龍匯道 添華道 通訊員需要舉起<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">綠色</span>+ D牌 </span>等全場有所準備<br />\n<br />\n最起碼應該有[size=5]六至八組通訊員揸旗<br />\n天橋上面都應該配備一組<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">建議3</span></span><br />\n<br />\n每個攤位應該配備嘉年華地圖hard copy<br />\n方便攤位主持人調配人力物資 <br />\nMark低各資源站 <br />\n甚至plan primary, secondary 遊戲路障<br />\n亦方便哨兵視察環境後統一資料<br />\n<br />\n夢境見到上次嘉年華會有一份過咗膠嘅地圖<br />\n可以用marker畫完之後再刷走<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上次海洋公園嘉年華因為在場參加者通訊嚴重不足<br />\n好多人完全唔知發生乜嘢事所以冇準備<br />\n結果我哋好快被保安驅散<br />\n希望我哋準備得更好之後會做得更加好<br />\n真正贏到獎品"},{"pid":"c69759a3e823709e0c46e4d72e572b5c4d03d5b9","tid":1232956,"uid":191290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:59:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d6e4a271ffa38de2ac23ff6d95942ac180f8bfc8","tid":1232956,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:00:03.000Z","msg":"點解唔用手語"},{"pid":"f0e7d78d92cc986085335a8ce8484d0e9c3b550e","tid":1232956,"uid":191290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6e4a271ffa38de2ac23ff6d95942ac180f8bfc8","tid":1232956,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:00:03.000Z","msg":"點解唔用手語"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:00:34.000Z","msg":"因為希望在場所有人士都睇得明<br />\n唔係淨係旗手"},{"pid":"6e5401174aae6a2b675b3637abb3bf85528a